{"tid":1283973,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警犬雙重標準","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T07:58:24.000Z","uid":143093,"like":180,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"69047c4e9c95337d6c48d451678c27dd9ce73b5e","tid":1283973,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nU98fr4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnU98fr4.jpg&h=1e5f8e3c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2019年6月14, 香港警方出哂聲明叫人舉報網絡欺凌警犬嘅人<br />\n前兩日, 有隻警犬就擺個無辜市民上連登, 意圖想網絡欺凌佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大學狗公<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1273422\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1273422</a><br />\n<br />\n會員 無聊哥 #259424 俾人踢爆之後無再上過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我建議受害人立即報警, 務求找出真相<br />\n若果真係許sir擺你出嚟, 希望你可以告佢誹謗, 執法者知法犯法 理應比普通人判得更加重罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d23b6b0f7c627da2927ab2b226bc3ca60f0afb","tid":1283973,"uid":143093,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"阿sir 你個頭出完聲明叫人唔好犯法 個頭你地就犯法<br />\n呢啲算係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7973c1f79873a858851e5a3515b697e04131be2a","tid":1283973,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:45:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0079a746b5132216db5b30e9d855b8acacb68095","tid":1283973,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"你冇嘢講"},{"pid":"c07fe0c863c5c9f48444f63ad9f611c44c39df4f","tid":1283973,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6077745e8a1f8a39c2336170658d7d5d8910c2c1","tid":1283973,"uid":143093,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:48:01.000Z","msg":"宜家受害人因爲俾人亂咁屈而搞到心理受創，咁樣點算好？？"},{"pid"